data_table.description: Subject ID, age, gender, family history of breast cancer, and estrogen receptor status of samples obtained from participants with or without breast cancer and involved in the "Cancer Genetic Markers of Susceptibility (CGEMS) Breast Cancer Genome-wide Association Study (GWAS) - Primary Scan: Nurses' Health Study - Additional Cases: Nurses' Health Study 2" project.

variable.name: AGE
variable.description: Age at enrollment in 5 year interval

variable.name: FAMILY_HISTORY
variable.description: Family history, yes or no? [YES, NO]

variable.name: ER_STATUS
variable.description: Estrogen receptor status [POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, MISSING, NA]
